snippet.textDisplay:
The truth is:
Kaushiki Chakraborty refused to sing in Bollywood films. 
She did only a few as the part of her experimentation . 

She said in an interview that she loved to sing her own song, liked to express her own emotions in her own way 👍🏼👏🏼🙏🏽

And most importantly, she strongly believes in serving ‘Biriyani’ and not ‘Instant Noodles - Maggie’ to her music loving listeners 👍🏼👏🏼🙏🏽

snippet.textDisplay: Kaushiki Chakraborty is a class all her own. With respect, I don't think it is fair either to her or to Lata ji to compare them to one another. It is a case of apples and oranges. Lataji was supreme in the filmi songs while Kaushiki has no parallel in today's classical and semi-classical genre. Kaushiki weaves magic with her voice and unbelievable control over all chords. Please listen to her Meeru concert classical melodies. Absolutely mesmerizing. May she live long and happy.
snippet.textOriginal: Kaushiki Chakraborty is a class all her own. With respect, I don't think it is fair either to her or to Lata ji to compare them to one another. It is a case of apples and oranges. Lataji was supreme in the filmi songs while Kaushiki has no parallel in today's classical and semi-classical genre. Kaushiki weaves magic with her voice and unbelievable control over all chords. Please listen to her Meeru concert classical melodies. Absolutely mesmerizing. May she live long and happy.
